OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775859115
OL,3,CWoman injured in pony and trap crash
OL,4,Cin Kent dies in hospital
OL,6,FA woman who was injured in a collision
OL,7,Fwhile travelling in a pony and trap in
OL,8,FKent has died in hospital, the third
OL,9,Fperson to die in the incident.
OL,11,FEmergency services were called to the
OL,12,FA228 Boyle Way, between the junctions
OL,13,Fof Bandridges Road and Hale Street, in
OL,14,FEast Peckham near Tonbridge at 6.25pm
OL,15,Fon Wednesday 1 April.
OL,17,FA white DAF tipper truck was being
OL,18,Fdriven on the southbound carriageway
OL,19,Fwhen it was involved in a collision
OL,20,Fwith a pony and trap travelling in the
OL,21,Fsame direction.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G1/4
