PN,41302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775859115
OL,3,CWoman injured in pony and trap crash
OL,4,Cin Kent dies in hospital
OL,6,FA man who was in the trap died at the
OL,7,Fscene.
OL,9,FA woman and young girl who had also
OL,10,Fbeen riding in the trap were taken
OL,11,Fhospital. The young girl was confirmed
OL,12,Fdead at hospital and the woman was
OL,13,Fconfirmed dead on Thursday 9 April.
OL,15,FThe pony also died at the scene.
OL,17,FThe driver of the tipper, a 29-year-
OL,18,Fold man from Kent, was arrested on
OL,19,Fsuspicion of causing death and serious
OL,20,Finjury by dangerous driving and
OL,21,Fdriving whilst unfit.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/4
OL,2,W,.!" ,.!+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext PageBS-SE Eng NewsCThis DayFReg TV
FL,414,410,120,260,000,100
PN,41303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F413A1775859115
OL,3,CWoman injured in pony and trap crash
OL,4,Cin Kent dies in hospital
OL,6,FHe was taken into custody and has
OL,7,Fsince been released on bail pending
OL,8,Ffurther enquiries.
OL,10,FA Kent Police spokesperson said: "An
OL,11,Finvestigation into the circumstances
OL,12,Fis underway and officers are
OL,13,Fcontinuing to urge any witnesses or
OL,14,Fanyone who saw the truck or pony and
OL,15,Ftrap prior to the collision, to
OL,16,Fcontact the appeal line.
OL,18,F"Call the Serious Collision
OL,19,FInvestigation Unit on 01622 798538,
OL,20,Fquoting reference BN/JG/027/26.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G3/4
